  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK853">
<l>ikaleṉṉu mevvanōy nīkkiṉ ṟavalillāt</l>
<l>tāvil viḷakkan tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To rid one-self of the distressing disease of hatred will bestow (on one) a never-decreasing imperishable fame.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
